snippet.title: Cat Quest III - Opening Animation
snippet.description:
All paws on deck! 

Our furriest adventure yet is on the horizon. Here is a sneak peek into the opening animation of Cat Quest III, the latest instalment of our feline-franchise. 

Take to the seas with our fearless captain and embark on a quest for treasure, treats, and purr-fect plunder. Take a closer look at some of the gameplay, and hello to some new and returning characters! 

So hoist the anchor and prepare to set sail on PS5, PS4, Nintendo Switch™, Xbox One and Xbox Series X|S and PC (via STEAM) this year! 

Wishlist meow! 

http://catquestgame.com/
